%D Usage:
%D
%D \starttyping
%D \setmathfunctionstyle\fontstyle % or {rm} or {ss} or ..
%D \rm test $\sin{(x^{\sin(x^{\sin(x)})})}$ test
%D \ss test $\sin{(x^{\sin(x^{\sin(x)})})}$ test
